1- Download Virtual Box from : https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads
2- Download Ubuntu 18.04 (codenamed Bionic Beaver) : https://phoenixnap.com/kb/how-to-install-ubuntu-18-04
once downloaded Ubuntu you will get an ISO file so either burn it on Flash USB or run it using the Virtual Box

so for running it on the Virtual Box , you will open the program and then 
- Press New , Name the Virtual system and then you will choose the ISO file you downloaded for Ubuntu

3- Now the Virtual Box will install the Ubuntu and you will have to create a username and password for Ubuntu system later on

after that you are ready to go and use Ubuntu 
